<item>
            <title>[LU-1521] What&apos;s the &quot;best&quot; default stripe count</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1521</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Dear support, &lt;br/&gt;
  I&apos;d like to know if there&apos;s a kind of &quot;best practice&quot; regarding the default stripe count to set on the Lustre file system. &lt;br/&gt;
I noticed that, based on the hardware we are using, having a stripe count to 24 often create problem simply untaring a file, instead having a stripe count to 4 seems to improve the situation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do you have any suggestion of how to understand what&apos;s best stripe count to set and how to suggest to our users how to deal with that?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;br/&gt;
Fabio &lt;/p&gt;</description>
